headline: Aytu BioPharma Inc. (AYTU) Reports Q1 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Aytu BioPharma (AYTU) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -33.33% and +10.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
